{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":788,"text":"What I want to do this afternoon"},{"time":2415,"text":"is something a little different than what's scheduled."},{"time":5280,"text":"Foreign policy, you can figure that out"},{"time":7226,"text":"by watching, I don't know, Rachel Maddow or somebody,"},{"time":10260,"text":"but — (Laughter) —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12094,"text":"I want to talk about young people and structure,"},{"time":15656,"text":"young people and structure."},{"time":17623,"text":"This was last Wednesday afternoon"},{"time":19871,"text":"at a school in Brooklyn, New York,"},{"time":22375,"text":"at Cristo Rey High School, run by the Jesuits."},{"time":25309,"text":"And I was talking to this group of students, and take a look at them."},{"time":29146,"text":"They were around me in three directions."},{"time":31613,"text":"You'll noticed that almost all of them are minority."},{"time":34409,"text":"You'll notice that the building is rather austere."},{"time":36254,"text":"It's an old New York school building, nothing fancy."},{"time":40385,"text":"They still have old blackboards and whatnot."},{"time":42916,"text":"And there are about 300 kids in this school,"},{"time":45507,"text":"and the school's been going now for four years,"},{"time":48159,"text":"and they're about to graduate their first class."},{"time":51113,"text":"Twenty-two people are graduating,"},{"time":53184,"text":"and all 22 are going to college."},{"time":55427,"text":"They all come from homes where there is, for the most part,"},{"time":58167,"text":"just one person in the home,"},{"time":60690,"text":"usually the mother or the grandmother, and that's it,"},{"time":63596,"text":"and they come here for their education"},{"time":66083,"text":"and for their structure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67496,"text":"Now I had this picture taken, and it was put up"},{"time":70304,"text":"on my Facebook page last week,"},{"time":72797,"text":"and somebody wrote in,"},{"time":74431,"text":"\"Huh, why does he have him standing at attention like that?\""},{"time":79417,"text":"And then they said, \"But he looks good.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83788,"text":"He does look good, because kids need structure,"},{"time":86498,"text":"and the trick I play in all of my school appearances"},{"time":90004,"text":"is that when I get through with my little homily to the kids,"},{"time":92903,"text":"I then invite them to ask questions,"},{"time":95087,"text":"and when they raise their hands, I say, \"Come up,\""},{"time":96952,"text":"and I make them come up and stand in front of me."},{"time":99291,"text":"I make them stand at attention like a soldier."},{"time":101405,"text":"Put your arms straight down at your side,"},{"time":103187,"text":"look up, open your eyes, stare straight ahead,"},{"time":106639,"text":"and speak out your question loudly so everybody can hear."},{"time":110074,"text":"No slouching, no pants hanging down, none of that stuff."},{"time":113331,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":114702,"text":"And this young man, his name is -- his last name Cruz --"},{"time":117967,"text":"he loved it. That's all over his Facebook page and it's gone viral."},{"time":121804,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":123991,"text":"So people think I'm being unkind to this kid."},{"time":126734,"text":"No, we're having a little fun."},{"time":128378,"text":"And the thing about it, I've done this for years,"},{"time":130792,"text":"the younger they are, the more fun it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133952,"text":"When I get six- and seven-year-olds in a group,"},{"time":136892,"text":"I have to figure out how to keep them quiet."},{"time":138771,"text":"You know that they'll always start yakking."},{"time":140774,"text":"And so I play a little game with them"},{"time":142379,"text":"before I make them stand at attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143951,"text":"I say, \"Now listen. In the army,"},{"time":146224,"text":"when we want you to pay attention,"},{"time":148552,"text":"we have a command. It's called 'at ease.'"},{"time":151737,"text":"It means everybody be quiet and pay attention. Listen up."},{"time":155311,"text":"Do you understand?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":156449,"text":"\"Uh-huh, uh-huh, uh-huh.\"\"Let's practice. Everybody start chatting.\""},{"time":161314,"text":"And I let them go for about 10 seconds, then I go, \"At ease!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":164611,"text":"\"Huh!\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168116,"text":"\"Yes, General. Yes, General.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170638,"text":"Try it with your kids. See if it works. (Laughter)"},{"time":173041,"text":"I don't think so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176094,"text":"But anyway, it's a game I play, and it comes obviously"},{"time":179108,"text":"from my military experience."},{"time":180830,"text":"Because for the majority of my adult life,"},{"time":184259,"text":"I worked with young kids, teenagers with guns, I call them."},{"time":188319,"text":"And we would bring them into the army,"},{"time":190764,"text":"and the first thing we would do is to put them"},{"time":193213,"text":"in an environment of structure, put them in ranks,"},{"time":197300,"text":"make them all wear the same clothes,"},{"time":198723,"text":"cut all their hair off so they look alike,"},{"time":201217,"text":"make sure that they are standing in ranks."},{"time":203421,"text":"We teach them how to go right face, left face,"},{"time":205201,"text":"so they can obey instructions and know"},{"time":207118,"text":"the consequences of not obeying instructions."},{"time":210046,"text":"It gives them structure."},{"time":211511,"text":"And then we introduce them to somebody who they come to hate immediately, the drill sergeant."},{"time":215691,"text":"And they hate him."},{"time":217565,"text":"And the drill sergeant starts screaming at them,"},{"time":219913,"text":"and telling them to do all kinds of awful things."},{"time":223762,"text":"But then the most amazing thing happens over time."},{"time":226766,"text":"Once that structure is developed,"},{"time":229792,"text":"once they understand the reason for something,"},{"time":233010,"text":"once they understand, \"Mama ain't here, son."},{"time":237016,"text":"I'm your worst nightmare. I'm your daddy and your mommy."},{"time":240836,"text":"And that's just the way it is. You got that, son?"},{"time":243448,"text":"Yeah, and then when I ask you a question, there are only three possible answers:"},{"time":246286,"text":"yes, sir; no, sir; and no excuse, sir."},{"time":248682,"text":"Don't start telling me why you didn't do something."},{"time":250845,"text":"It's yes, sir; no, sir; no excuse, sir.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":253497,"text":"\"You didn't shave.\"\"But sir —\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":254620,"text":"\"No, don't tell me how often you scraped your face this morning."},{"time":257875,"text":"I'm telling you you didn't shave.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":259615,"text":"\"No excuse, sir.\"\"Attaboy, you're learning fast.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":262821,"text":"But you'd be amazed at what you can do with them"},{"time":265209,"text":"once you put them in that structure."},{"time":267663,"text":"In 18 weeks, they have a skill. They are mature."},{"time":272521,"text":"And you know what, they come to admire the drill sergeant"},{"time":275638,"text":"and they never forget the drill sergeant."},{"time":277536,"text":"They come to respect him."},{"time":280171,"text":"And so we need more of this kind of structure and respect"},{"time":284086,"text":"in the lives of our children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286117,"text":"I spend a lot of time with youth groups,"},{"time":288090,"text":"and I say to people, \"When does the education process begin?\""},{"time":291381,"text":"We're always talking about, \"Let's fix the schools."},{"time":293060,"text":"Let's do more for our teachers. Let's put more computers in our schools."},{"time":296807,"text":"Let's get it all online.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":299748,"text":"That isn't the whole answer. It's part of the answer."},{"time":303054,"text":"But the real answer begins with bringing a child to the school"},{"time":306316,"text":"with structure in that child's heart and soul to begin with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310924,"text":"When does the learning process begin? Does it begin in first grade?"},{"time":313793,"text":"No, no, it begins the first time"},{"time":315976,"text":"a child in a mother's arms"},{"time":318657,"text":"looks up at the mother"},{"time":321421,"text":"and says, \"Oh, this must be my mother."},{"time":324785,"text":"She's the one who feeds me."},{"time":327158,"text":"Oh yeah, when I don't feel so good down there,"},{"time":329364,"text":"she takes care of me."},{"time":331878,"text":"It's her language I will learn.\""},{"time":334901,"text":"And at that moment they shut out all the other languages"},{"time":337650,"text":"that they could be learning at that age,"},{"time":340006,"text":"but by three months, that's her."},{"time":342955,"text":"And if the person doing it, whether it's the mother"},{"time":345275,"text":"or grandmother, whoever's doing it,"},{"time":347268,"text":"that is when the education process begins."},{"time":349482,"text":"That's when language begins."},{"time":351210,"text":"That's when love begins. That's when structure begins."},{"time":353459,"text":"That's when you start to imprint on the child"},{"time":355947,"text":"that \"you are special,"},{"time":358165,"text":"you are different from every other child in the world."},{"time":361354,"text":"And we're going to read to you.\""},{"time":363438,"text":"A child who has not been read to"},{"time":365509,"text":"is in danger when that child gets to school."},{"time":367653,"text":"A child who doesn't know his or her colors"},{"time":369713,"text":"or doesn't know how to tell time, doesn't know how to tie shoes,"},{"time":372727,"text":"doesn't know how to do those things,"},{"time":374126,"text":"and doesn't know how to do something that"},{"time":376796,"text":"goes by a word that was drilled into me as a kid: mind."},{"time":379672,"text":"Mind your manners! Mind your adults! Mind what you're saying!"},{"time":383560,"text":"This is the way children are raised properly."},{"time":387083,"text":"And I watched my own young grandchildren now come along"},{"time":389878,"text":"and they're, much to the distress of my children,"},{"time":393971,"text":"they are acting just like we did. You know? You imprint them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398647,"text":"And that's what you have to do to prepare children for education and for school."},{"time":403872,"text":"And I'm working at all the energy I have"},{"time":406131,"text":"to sort of communicate this message that"},{"time":408461,"text":"we need preschool, we need Head Start,"},{"time":412340,"text":"we need prenatal care."},{"time":414860,"text":"The education process begins even before the child is born,"},{"time":419075,"text":"and if you don't do that, you're going to have difficulty."},{"time":421783,"text":"And we are having difficulties in so many of our communities"},{"time":424197,"text":"and so many of our schools where kids are coming"},{"time":427242,"text":"to first grade and their eyes are blazing,"},{"time":429553,"text":"they've got their little knapsack on and they're ready to go,"},{"time":433164,"text":"and then they realize they're not like the other first graders"},{"time":436565,"text":"who know books, have been read to, can do their alphabet."},{"time":441029,"text":"And by the third grade, the kids who didn't have"},{"time":443723,"text":"that structure and minding in the beginning"},{"time":447869,"text":"start to realize they're behind, and what do they do?"},{"time":449779,"text":"They act it out. They act it out, and they're on their way"},{"time":453100,"text":"to jail or they're on their way to being dropouts."},{"time":456186,"text":"It's predictable."},{"time":458050,"text":"If you're not at the right reading level at third grade,"},{"time":461016,"text":"you are a candidate for jail at age 18,"},{"time":465093,"text":"and we have the highest incarceration rate"},{"time":467330,"text":"because we're not getting our kids the proper start in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470258,"text":"The last chapter in my book is called"},{"time":472474,"text":"\"The Gift of a Good Start.\""},{"time":475385,"text":"The gift of a good start. Every child ought to have a good start in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479077,"text":"I was privileged to have that kind of good start."},{"time":481780,"text":"I was not a great student."},{"time":483671,"text":"I was a public school kid in New York City,"},{"time":486339,"text":"and I didn't do well at all."},{"time":488979,"text":"I have my entire New York City Board of Education transcript"},{"time":492791,"text":"from kindergarten through college."},{"time":495234,"text":"I wanted it when I was writing my first book."},{"time":497504,"text":"I wanted to see if my memory was correct,"},{"time":499543,"text":"and, my God, it was. (Laughter)"},{"time":502818,"text":"Straight C everywhere."},{"time":505606,"text":"And I finally bounced through high school,"},{"time":508047,"text":"got into the City College of New York"},{"time":510126,"text":"with a 78.3 average, which I shouldn't have been allowed in with,"},{"time":513766,"text":"and then I started out in engineering,"},{"time":516505,"text":"and that only lasted six months. (Laughter)"},{"time":519063,"text":"And then I went into geology, \"rocks for jocks.\" This is easy."},{"time":523076,"text":"And then I found ROTC."},{"time":525078,"text":"I found something that I did well and something that I loved doing,"},{"time":529012,"text":"and I found a group of youngsters like me who felt the same way."},{"time":532906,"text":"And so my whole life then was dedicated to ROTC and the military."},{"time":536892,"text":"And I say to young kids everywhere, as you're growing up"},{"time":539560,"text":"and as this structure is being developed inside of you,"},{"time":542161,"text":"always be looking for that which you do well and that which you love doing,"},{"time":545197,"text":"and when you find those two things together, man, you got it."},{"time":548334,"text":"That's what's going on. And that's what I found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550698,"text":"Now the authorities at CCNY were getting tired of me being there."},{"time":553352,"text":"I'd been there four and a half going on five years,"},{"time":555153,"text":"and my grades were not doing particularly well,"},{"time":559563,"text":"and I was in occasional difficulties with the administration."},{"time":562705,"text":"And so they said, \"But he does so well in ROTC."},{"time":565619,"text":"Look, he gets straight A's in that but not in anything else.\""},{"time":568969,"text":"And so they said, \"Look, let's take his ROTC grades"},{"time":573325,"text":"and roll them into his overall GPA and see what happens.\""},{"time":576771,"text":"And they did, and it brought me up to 2.0. (Laughter)"},{"time":583487,"text":"Yep. (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":587221,"text":"They said, \"It's good enough for government work."},{"time":590270,"text":"Give him to the army. We'll never see him again. We'll never see him again.\""},{"time":593768,"text":"So they shipped me off to the army,"},{"time":595620,"text":"and lo and behold, many years later,"},{"time":599288,"text":"I'm considered one of the greatest sons the City College of New York has ever had. (Laughter)"},{"time":603594,"text":"So, I tell young people everywhere,"},{"time":606796,"text":"it ain't where you start in life, it's what you do with life"},{"time":610987,"text":"that determines where you end up in life,"},{"time":614598,"text":"and you are blessed to be living in a country that,"},{"time":617283,"text":"no matter where you start, you have opportunities"},{"time":620469,"text":"so long as you believe in yourself,"},{"time":623173,"text":"you believe in the society and the country,"},{"time":626164,"text":"and you believe that you can self-improve"},{"time":629583,"text":"and educate yourself as you go along."},{"time":631994,"text":"And that's the key to success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634227,"text":"But it begins with the gift of a good start."},{"time":637577,"text":"If we don't give that gift to each and every one of our kids,"},{"time":640050,"text":"if we don't invest at the earliest age,"},{"time":643728,"text":"we're going to be running into difficulties."},{"time":646470,"text":"It's why we have a dropout rate of roughly 25 percent overall"},{"time":650736,"text":"and almost 50 percent of our minority population"},{"time":653458,"text":"living in low-income areas,"},{"time":656932,"text":"because they're not getting the gift of a good start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659713,"text":"My gift of a good start was not only being in a nice family,"},{"time":663691,"text":"a good family, but having a family that said to me,"},{"time":667246,"text":"\"Now listen, we came to this country in banana boats"},{"time":671193,"text":"in 1920 and 1924."},{"time":674555,"text":"We worked like dogs down in the garment industry every single day."},{"time":678730,"text":"We're not doing it so that you can stick something up your nose"},{"time":682256,"text":"or get in trouble. And don't even think about dropping out.\""},{"time":686636,"text":"If I had ever gone home and told those immigrant people"},{"time":689687,"text":"that, \"You know, I'm tired of school and I'm dropping out,\""},{"time":692156,"text":"they'd said, \"We're dropping you out. We'll get another kid.\""},{"time":694813,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":701171,"text":"They had expectations for all of the cousins"},{"time":703697,"text":"and the extended family of immigrants that lived in the South Bronx,"},{"time":707280,"text":"but they had more than just expectations for us."},{"time":710439,"text":"They stuck into our hearts like a dagger"},{"time":714350,"text":"a sense of shame: \"Don't you shame this family.\""},{"time":719212,"text":"Sometimes I would get in trouble,"},{"time":720875,"text":"and my parents were coming home,"},{"time":722718,"text":"and I was in my room waiting for what's going to happen,"},{"time":726199,"text":"and I would sit there saying to myself, \"Okay, look,"},{"time":728410,"text":"take the belt and hit me, but, God, don't give me that 'shame the family' bit again.\""},{"time":733185,"text":"It devastated me when my mother did that to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":735942,"text":"And I also had this extended network."},{"time":738106,"text":"Children need a network. Children need to be part of a tribe,"},{"time":741094,"text":"a family, a community."},{"time":742975,"text":"In my case it was aunts who lived in all of these tenement buildings."},{"time":747199,"text":"I don't know how many of you are New Yorkers,"},{"time":749055,"text":"but there were these tenement buildings,"},{"time":750976,"text":"and these women were always hanging out one of the windows,"},{"time":754189,"text":"leaning on a pillow."},{"time":755811,"text":"They never left. (Laughter)"},{"time":758570,"text":"I, so help me God, I grew up walking those streets,"},{"time":761604,"text":"and they were always there."},{"time":763086,"text":"They never went to the bathroom. They never cooked. (Laughter)"},{"time":765960,"text":"They never did anything."},{"time":768506,"text":"But what they did was keep us in play."},{"time":771219,"text":"They kept us in play."},{"time":773505,"text":"And they didn't care"},{"time":775763,"text":"whether you became a doctor or a lawyer or a general,"},{"time":780510,"text":"and they never expected any generals in the family,"},{"time":783603,"text":"as long as you got an education and then you got a job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787463,"text":"\"Don't give us any of that self-actualization stuff."},{"time":789454,"text":"You get a job and get out of the house."},{"time":792269,"text":"We don't have time to waste for that."},{"time":794747,"text":"And then you can support us. That's the role of you guys.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":798322,"text":"And so, it's so essential that we kind of put this culture"},{"time":803844,"text":"back into our families, all families."},{"time":808126,"text":"And it is so important that all of you here today"},{"time":811461,"text":"who are successful people,"},{"time":814137,"text":"and I'm sure have wonderful families and children and grandchildren,"},{"time":818692,"text":"it's not enough. You've got to reach out and back"},{"time":820430,"text":"and find kids like Mr. Cruz"},{"time":823081,"text":"who can make it if you give them the structure,"},{"time":826451,"text":"if you reach back and help, if you mentor,"},{"time":828438,"text":"if you invest in boys and girls clubs,"},{"time":830812,"text":"if you work with your school system,"},{"time":832703,"text":"make sure it's the best school system,"},{"time":833977,"text":"and not just your kid's school, but the school uptown in Harlem,"},{"time":838800,"text":"not just downtown Montessori on the West Side."},{"time":841622,"text":"All of us have to have a commitment to do that."},{"time":845775,"text":"And we're not just investing in the kids."},{"time":848425,"text":"We're investing in our future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850478,"text":"We're going to be a minority-majority country"},{"time":853299,"text":"in one more generation."},{"time":855292,"text":"Those that we call minorities now are going to be the majority."},{"time":858661,"text":"And we have to make sure that they are ready to be the majority."},{"time":861241,"text":"We have to make sure they're ready to be the leaders"},{"time":863472,"text":"of this great country of ours,"},{"time":866424,"text":"a country that is like no other,"},{"time":869900,"text":"a country that amazes me every single day,"},{"time":871585,"text":"a country that's fractious. We're always arguing with each other."},{"time":874205,"text":"That's how the system's supposed to work."},{"time":877177,"text":"It's a country of such contrasts, but it's a nation of nations."},{"time":880756,"text":"We touch every nation. Every nation touches us."},{"time":884752,"text":"We are a nation of immigrants."},{"time":886437,"text":"That's why we need sound immigration policy."},{"time":889581,"text":"It's ridiculous not to have a sound immigration policy"},{"time":892816,"text":"to welcome those who want to come here and be part of this great nation,"},{"time":895899,"text":"or we can send back home with an education"},{"time":898052,"text":"to help their people rise up out of poverty."},{"time":901433,"text":"One of the great stories I love to tell is about my love"},{"time":905276,"text":"of going to my hometown of New York"},{"time":906673,"text":"and walking up Park Avenue on a beautiful day"},{"time":908467,"text":"and admiring everything and seeing all the people go by"},{"time":910948,"text":"from all over the world."},{"time":912402,"text":"But what I always have to do is stop at one of the corners"},{"time":916040,"text":"and get a hot dog from the immigrant pushcart peddler."},{"time":919426,"text":"Gotta have a dirty water dog. (Laughter)"},{"time":922577,"text":"And no matter where I am or what I'm doing,"},{"time":925557,"text":"I've got to do that."},{"time":926832,"text":"I even did it when I was Secretary of State."},{"time":929497,"text":"I'd come out of my suite at the Waldorf Astoria"},{"time":932398,"text":"— (Laughter) —"},{"time":935478,"text":"be walking up the street, and I would hit around 55th Street"},{"time":938789,"text":"looking for the immigrant pushcart peddler."},{"time":941100,"text":"In those days, I had five bodyguards around me"},{"time":943299,"text":"and three New York City police cars would roll alongside"},{"time":946193,"text":"to make sure nobody whacked me while I was going up Park Avenue. (Laughter)"},{"time":951013,"text":"And I would order the hot dog from the guy,"},{"time":952681,"text":"and he'd start to fix it, and then he'd look around"},{"time":955127,"text":"at the bodyguards and the police cars --"},{"time":956804,"text":"\"I've got a green card! I've got a green card!\" (Laughter)"},{"time":958886,"text":"\"It's okay, it's okay.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":963222,"text":"But now I'm alone. I'm alone."},{"time":965670,"text":"I've got no bodyguards, I've got no police cars. I've got nothing."},{"time":968461,"text":"But I gotta have my hot dog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971123,"text":"I did it just last week. It was on a Tuesday evening"},{"time":974887,"text":"down by Columbus Circle."},{"time":977187,"text":"And the scene repeats itself so often."},{"time":980042,"text":"I'll go up and ask for my hot dog,"},{"time":983396,"text":"and the guy will fix it, and as he's finishing,"},{"time":985758,"text":"he'll say, \"I know you. I see you on television."}]},{"cues":[{"time":988460,"text":"You're, well, you're General Powell.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":990354,"text":"\"Yes, yes.\"\"Oh ... \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":993044,"text":"I hand him the money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":994195,"text":"\"No, General. You can't pay me. I've been paid."},{"time":999120,"text":"America has paid me. I never forget where I came from."},{"time":1002883,"text":"But now I'm an American. Sir, thank you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006073,"text":"I accept the generosity, continue up the street,"},{"time":1008341,"text":"and it washes over me, my God,"},{"time":1010570,"text":"it's the same country that greeted my parents this way 90 years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014588,"text":"So we are still that magnificent country,"},{"time":1016775,"text":"but we are fueled by young people coming up"},{"time":1019550,"text":"from every land in the world,"},{"time":1022554,"text":"and it is our obligation as contributing citizens"},{"time":1026081,"text":"to this wonderful country of ours"},{"time":1027867,"text":"to make sure that no child gets left behind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1031014,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033092,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}